DEPRECATION WARNING [bogus-combinators]: The selector "a +" is only valid for nesting and shouldn't
have children other than style rules. It will be omitted from the generated CSS.
This will be an error in Dart Sass 2.0.0.

More info: https://sass-lang.com/d/bogus-combinators

  ,
1 | a + {
  | ^^^ invalid selector
2 |   b: c;
  |   ==== this is not a style rule
  '
    deprecation-bogus-combinators.scss 1:1  root stylesheet

